                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Objectives
                        %h3 Revewing Project Goals
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p Island Finance's business goals around conversion and digital adoption were only achievable if the site actually worked for the people visiting it. The goal was to identify where those interests converged and design toward that intersection.
                        .project-goals__graph
                            .columns
