        .case-study__brainstorming
            .anchor#brainstorming
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Brainstorming
                        %h3 Organizing Ideas & the Solution
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p
                            Insights from research and personas were categorized into four areas to guide the design direction and feature decisions.
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Opportunities
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Biggest personal loan specialist on the island
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p 49 branches as a trust and reach asset
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Strong brand recognition since 1959
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Underserved digital self-service market
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Financial literacy content gap accross competitors
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Mobile-first audience with growing digital habits
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p 24 hour decision
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Pain Points
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p APR and total cost not visible upfront
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Finalizing an application & managing a loan requires branch visits
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Application process has too many friction points
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Financial jargon with no explanation
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Site is slow and breaks on mobile
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p No payment calculator before applying
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Hidden pages both on desktop and mobile
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Considerations
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Financial content must comply with PR lending regulations
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Spanish-dominant audience requires bilingual content
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Many users have low financial literacy, plain language is required
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Trust must be established before the application flow begins
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Branch network should complement, not compete with, digital
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Solutions
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Transparent APR and cost displayed on every loan page
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Loan calculator accessible from homepage
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Digital loan management dashboard
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Plain-language glossary for financial terms
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Step-by-step application with progress indicators
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Branch finder integrated into website
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Offer ability to submit documents digitally and receive direct deposit without visiting branch
        .case-study__features
            .anchor#features
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Feature Roadmap
                        %h3 Transforming Needs into Features
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p
                            Informed by user research, competitive gaps, and project goals, this feature set prioritizes experiences that build trust, reduce friction, and make personal lending accessible and transparent for all borrowers.
                .features__features-table
                    %table
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Page / Feature
                                %th Priority
                                %th Description
                                %th Goal
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td Homepage
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Clear value proposition, loan calculator above the fold, visible trust signals, prominent CTA to start application. Bilingual EN/ES toggle persistent throughout.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Loan Calculator
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Interactive calculator allowing users to set loan amount and term, instantly showing monthly payment and total cost. Accessible from homepage and all loan product pages.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                                    %br
                                    %span.education Financial Literacy
                            %tr
                                %td Personal loans page
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Transparent APR range displayed upfront, clear eligibility requirements, plain-language explanation of how interest works, and a step-by-step guide to the application process before any form fields appear.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Application flow
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Step-by-step application with a clear progress indicator, plain-language form labels, contextual help text, document upload capability, and a clear timeline for approval. Mobile-optimized throughout.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.digital Digital First
                            %tr
                                %td Navigation
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Simple top navigation with loan products, branch finder, account login, and apply CTA always visible. Bilingual toggle persistent. No more than two levels of depth.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.digital Digital First
                            %tr
                                %td Branch finder
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Interactive map of all 49 Puerto Rico branches with address, hours, phone, and directions. As a stand alone page and integrated into the application flow as an option for users who want to complete documentation in person.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Account dashboard
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Digital loan management portal: balance, payment history, next due date, and online payment capability. Reduces branch traffic for routine tasks and is the most requested feature among existing customers.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.digital Digital First
                                    %br
                                    %span.retention Retention
                            %tr
                                %td Financial literacy hub
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Educational content covering how personal loans work, APR explained plainly, debt consolidation guide, and a financial glossary. Positions Island Finance as a trustworthy partner, not just a lender.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                                    %br
                                    %span.education Financial Literacy
                            %tr
                                %td Payment reminders
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Email and SMS payment reminders before due dates, opt-in from the account dashboard. Directly addresses one of the most cited friction points in user feedback.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.digital Digital First
                                    %br
                                    %span.retention Retention
                            %tr
                                %td Debt consolidation tool
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p3 P3 — Nice to Have
                                %td Interactive tool where users enter existing credit card balances and rates to see how much they would save consolidating into an Island Finance loan.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.education Financial Literacy
                                    %br
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                            %tr
                                %td Live chat support
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p3 P3 — Nice to Have
                                %td Chat widget available during business hours for users with questions mid-application. Reduces abandonment for users who get stuck rather than calling a branch or leaving the site entirely.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.conversion Drive Conversion
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
        
